      "Magazine articles often promise to tell you whether an Aries is compatible with a Libra. The astrological reality is infinitely more nuanced. Two people of the same sign can experience a conflictual relationship, while two signs reputed as incompatible can form a fulfilling couple for decades. The Sun sign describes only a fraction of your relational identity. To understand compatibility, you must look much deeper.",
      "In relationship astrology, Venus and Mars play a central role. Venus describes the way you love, what you find beautiful, how you express affection. Mars describes your desire, how you initiate intimacy, your sexual energy. A couple where Venus and Mars form harmonic or creatively tense aspects will experience immediate chemistry, regardless of their Sun signs. Two Venuses in compatible signs create a tacit understanding of what nourishes the other's heart.",
